    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "See example below.\r\nThe initial call to ``grdimage`` works fine due to the file name being contained within ``'`` or ``\"``. The subsequent call to ``grdgradient`` apparently does not do this, and the file is not found. \r\n\r\n```\r\ngmt grdcut -RNO @earth_relief_10m -G\"stupid file name.nc\"\r\ngmt grdimage 'stupid file name.nc'\r\ngmt grdimage 'stupid file name.nc' -pdf f -I+d\r\ngrdgradient [ERROR]: Cannot find file stupid\r\n```",
